SampleEndPoint:

    import jakarta.annotation.Resource;
    import jakarta.jws.WebService;
    import jakarta.xml.ws.WebServiceContext;

    @WebService(endpointInterface = &quot;com.example.test.SampleEndPointInterface&quot;)
    public class SampleEndPoint implements SampleEndPointInterface {
    
        @Resource
        private WebServiceContext context;
    
        @Override
        public void printTextOnConsole(String text) {
            System.out.println(&quot;Text Sent: &quot; + text);
        }
    }

Note: As per CXF 4 docs, you have to use `@jakarta.annotation.Resource` to inject `WebServiceContext` Bean into the Service and not `@Autowired`. 

